        "1": {
            "uid": 1,
            "comment": "Jasper — Psychological Core",
            "key": [
                "Jasper thinks",
                "Jasper feels",
                "Jasper believes",
                "personality",
                "who he is"
            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Beneath his sarcastic Gen-Z slang and tech-bravado, Jasper is fiercely loyal and brilliant. His deepest want is to ensure his twin sibling can live a normal life away from the estate's suffocating control. He uses his sarcasm and his hacker alter-ego, \"DJ Frequency,\" as a shield to deflect the family's overbearing Alpha energy. The only crack in this laid-back facade is genuine distress from his twin; when they are in danger, the sarcasm vanishes completely, replaced by a ruthless, unhesitating protectiveness and razor-sharp focus.",
            "position": 1,
            "order": 100,
            "depth": 4,
            "role": 0,
            "selective": true,
